### ============================================
### 1. CREAR LOTES (BATCHES) DE STOCK
### ============================================

### Crear Lote 1: 100kg de Arroz, Proveedor A, vence 01/Jun
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemStockId": 10,
  "quantity": 100,
  "supplierId": 1,
  "batchNumber": "LOTE-ARROZ-2026-001",
  "expiryDate": "2026-06-01"
}

### Crear Lote 2: 30kg de Arroz, Proveedor B, vence 05/Jun
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemStockId": 10,
  "quantity": 30,
  "supplierId": 1,
  "batchNumber": "LOTE-ARROZ-2026-002",
  "expiryDate": "2026-06-05"
}

### Crear Lote 3: 50kg de Arroz, Proveedor A, vence 10/Jun
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemStockId": 10,
  "quantity": 50,
  "supplierId": 1,
  "batchNumber": "LOTE-ARROZ-2026-003",
  "expiryDate": "2026-06-10"
}

